                    <msContents class="lemmatic">
                        <summary><title type="general">شرح فصول أبقراط</title>
                            The manuscript contains the following works:
                            1) Introduction of Abd Latif Baghdadi's commentary on the Aphorisims in <locus n="1-2, 247">ff. 1-2, 247</locus>;
                            2) a part of Ibn Abi Ṣadiq's commentary on the Aphorisms in <locus n='3-31'>ff. 3-31</locus>;
                            3) Hunayn's Question on Medicine with Ibn Abi Ṣadiq's commentary in <locus n='31-246'>ff. 31-246</locus>.
                        
                        </summary>


